  //  0) default settings
  //  1) user's settings
  //  2) remote machine settings
  //  3) workspace settings  (this file)
  //  4) workspace folder settings
  //
  //
  // For details, see:
  // https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/getstarted/settings#_settings-precedence


